Jordan Flake brings nearly 20 years of focused estate planning experience to every engagement. He doesn't use templates or one-size-fits-all approaches. Every estate plan is built around your specific family, your specific assets, and your specific concerns.

Whether you need a straightforward will, a comprehensive trust-based plan, or complex asset protection strategies, Jordan works with you to ensure every detail is addressed — from beneficiary designations to healthcare directives to business succession.
